<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She recently went public with her new businessman boyfriend Mason Morfit after announcing her amicable split from her husband of 13 years earlier this year.</p>

<p>But Jordana Brewster was flying solo as she enjoyed an afternoon of shopping at the Brentwood Country Mart on Wednesday. </p>

<p>The actress, 40, cut a stylish figure in a strappy blue and white summer dress with spaghetti straps as she made her way back to her car.</p>

<p>Dressed to impress: Jordana Brewster cut a stylish figure in a strappy blue and white summer dress as she enjoyed an afternoon of shopping at the Brentwood Country Mart on Wednesday</p>

<p>The Fast And The Furious star displayed her natural good looks as she went make-up free, and wore her raven tresses in a natural straight style. </p>

<p>The mother-of-two opted for a chain link and stone necklace and accessorised with cream-framed glasses and a face mask. </p>

<p>Jordana wore a pair of patterned espadrilles and a straw tote bag as she made her way inside the shopping village. </p>

<p>Happy: The actress, 40, wore a pair of patterned espadrilles and a straw tote bag as she made her way inside the shopping village</p>

<p>The actress announced her 'amicable' split from her husband of 13 years, Andrew Form, earlier this year. </p>

<p>A source close to the couple told People magazine at the time: 'They have the utmost respect for each other. </p>

<p>'They remain committed to lovingly co-parent their two children as a team.' </p>

<p>The pair, who are parents to sons Julian, six, and Rowan, four, first met on the set of the horror movie The Texas Chainsaw Massacre: The Beginning, which he produced and she starred in. </p>

<p>On their one-year anniversary, he proposed with a 3.2-carat engagement ring and they wed in a private ceremony after a six-month engagement.</p>

<p>Just after filing for divorce, Jordana was seen passionately kissing her new CEO beau, Mason, 44, on a romantic stroll in Malibu. </p>

<p>Earlier this week, the actress posted their first official couple photo, with the two walking hand and hand from the ocean. </p>

<p>She captioned the comment with a red heart, as she looked over at her handsome man in the snap. </p>

<p>New love: The screen star recently went public with her new businessman boyfriend Mason Morfit after announcing her amicable split from her husband of 13 years earlier this year</p>
